    "However, most of these works do not utilize LLM's reasoning ability and cannot solve complex problems in clinical trials.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, our work is the first LLM agent work for clinical trials and is able to solve complex clinical trial reasoning problems.",
    "Methods Overview of ClinicalAgentOur proposed system is a conversational multi-agent framework analogous to a hospital staffed by various specialists.",
    "Each agent within this system plays a distinct role, mirroring the specialization seen in medical professionals-some focus on pharmacology, others on diagnosing diseases, while a few are dedicated to designing clinical trials.",
